GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed, reenacted, and amended as KRS 154.30-040, 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 178, sec. 17, effective July 15, 2008. -- Created 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 95, sec. 17, effective March 23, 2007.
